{"tid":1348741,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港銀行」我係一名小員工，呼籲同事自發罷工","createTime":"2019-07-22T08:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T06:54:41.000Z","uid":261166,"like":147,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"acb7ac69e46458202bc35a5533ae253c8eaf6bde","tid":1348741,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:50:14.000Z","msg":"相信香港仲有希望，相信企業仲有責任，<br />\n相信國際仲有公義，更相信連登的力量。<br />\n<br />\n以無比憤慨、悲痛寫出以下<span style=\"color: gold;\">罷工呼籲</span>，<br />\n希望<span style=\"color: gold;\">各行各業，齊心響應</span>。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n各位同事，<br />\n<br />\n香港法治，治安過去一個月嚴重破壞，<br />\n昨日（7月21日），元朗更發生恐怖襲擊，<br />\n超過四十平民百姓受襲。<br />\n今日，元朗屯門天水圍以至全港人心惶惶，<br />\n現在員工生命受威脅，精神受壓時，<br />\n無法專心工作，有重大困難為客戶提供專業服務。<br />\n<br />\n香港的核心價值受到前所未有的存亡威脅，<br />\n匯豐銀行作為本地及全球最大銀行之一，<br />\n本地最大僱主之一，香港作為集團最大盈利內源。<br />\n匯豐銀行最應該負起社會責任、道德責任，<br />\n為客戶、巿民、員工發聲，向政府表達巿民、客戶、員工的憂慮！<br />\n<br />\n現在部份工會已經呼籲員工注意安全，有需要時罷工；<br />\n另有商鋪、其他銀行亦已經因安全原因停止服務。　<br />\n<br />\n作為巿民，最大要求是家人安全，<br />\n作為員工，最大要求是工作安全，<br />\n作為客戶，我會明白體諒銀行停止服務。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我現呼籲所有<strong>香港（本地及在外）匯豐銀行的同事</strong>，即日起以個人身分參加罷工！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直至匯豐銀行管理層為社會向政府施壓及反映巿民訴求！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n亦借此呼籲香港各界及國際社會繼續關注香港民主自由人權受損，促請香港政府立即回應五大訴求，盡快回復正常秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqzyC6M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpqzyC6M.png&h=74027da6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"668b7a88b7a36c72a58869dd096a48a96af60de0","tid":1348741,"uid":257351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:57:45.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"4d240ce7579f9a01ea3fb6de6783336533c4691a","tid":1348741,"uid":202893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"956b11e5eeb8a9d43ccc0b59a501283139f76d4c","tid":1348741,"uid":132942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:59:22.000Z","msg":"一有黑社會斬人消息，元朗已經自發罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276d17dd64abf0cf05a45f8d56cc5aa07c06ca05","tid":1348741,"uid":262072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:01:06.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Bank - Raymond Cheng 好親中架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65596e94a7c7a2c18f646d7e39fa00244acab18d","tid":1348741,"uid":187698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"956b11e5eeb8a9d43ccc0b59a501283139f76d4c","tid":1348741,"uid":132942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:59:22.000Z","msg":"一有黑社會斬人消息，元朗已經自發罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:01:33.000Z","msg":"啲黑警咪就係身先士卒甘罷工 扮睇唔到聽唔到"},{"pid":"ac379e911d98a702a6a9606cfc2863e3fa22fea7","tid":1348741,"uid":279874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec679f107970b0928514010bc4eae8f0e9ae1c5b","tid":1348741,"uid":186827,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"佢地都有叫我地早D收工...<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9sZCmgN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9sZCmgN.png&h=93776989&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34d77a48ec6ebe71d309813b047d11e85a448c27","tid":1348741,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:03:16.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcc0f5fdedab69257298603cd76687f39e4ea8e","tid":1348741,"uid":261166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:03:33.000Z","msg":"希望有各行各業的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人</span></span>響應，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不在沉默中爆發，就在沉默中滅亡</span></span>"},{"pid":"7ef740376c60b4e588e553e306c57573f926cd8e","tid":1348741,"uid":160120,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:05:17.000Z","msg":"支持 前輩加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmbhmhX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmbhmhX.png&h=cc86c833&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fd9019bb9c7b5d1986212d97292e469099974b6","tid":1348741,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec679f107970b0928514010bc4eae8f0e9ae1c5b","tid":1348741,"uid":186827,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"佢地都有叫我地早D收工...<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9sZCmgN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9sZCmgN.png&h=93776989&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:18:29.000Z","msg":"匯豐銀行有更大道德同社會責任向政府建制施壓，<br />\n為香港發聲！"},{"pid":"59f5085192074ffed3f61e9ee8ed8f8a3b83dcc1","tid":1348741,"uid":283725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:21:32.000Z","msg":"你都係老屎忽。張証舊到發黃"},{"pid":"cc6a7bdb3acc04a4363eebf8cf9d7ddd421f136c","tid":1348741,"uid":277144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"148b4f5326153133cb991e756847e839d9287ad8","tid":1348741,"uid":257479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:27:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67b93bab2bc2482992df8d5cd9fcb2a483458341","tid":1348741,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:28:21.000Z","msg":